net.majorkernelpanic.streaming.video

Class H264Stream

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.majorkernelpanic.streaming.MediaStream

        • net.majorkernelpanic.streaming.video.H264Stream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Stream

    public class H264Stream
extends VideoStream
    A class for streaming H.264 from the camera of an android device using RTP. You should use a SpellCheckerService.Session instantiated with SessionBuilder instead of using this class directly. Call MediaStream.setDestinationAddress(InetAddress), MediaStream.setDestinationPorts(int) and VideoStream.setVideoQuality(VideoQuality) to configure the stream. You can then call start() to start the RTP stream. Call VideoStream.stop() to stop the stream.
